Package com.reactivecascade.reactive

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PersistentValue<T>
    A ReactiveValue which retains state between stops and starts of the application.
    ReactiveInteger
    An Integer which can be updated in an atomic, thread-safe manner.
    ReactiveLong
    A Long which can be updated in an atomic, thread-safe manner.
    ReactiveString
    A String which can be updated with various string operations in an atomic, thread-safe manner.
    ReactiveValue<T>
    Thread-safe reactive display of a variable getValue.
    Subscription<IN,OUT>
    This is the default implementation for a reactive active chain link.
